nodes.name: 1-aminocyclopropane-1-carboxylate oxygenase (ethylene-forming)
nodes.rxn: 1-Aminocyclopropane-1-carboxylate + Ascorbate + Oxygen <=> Ethylene + Cyanide ion + Dehydroascorbate + CO2 + 2 H2O

nodes.name: L-methionine:oxidized-thioredoxin S-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: L-Methionine + Thioredoxin disulfide + H2O <=> L-Methionine S-oxide + Thioredoxin

nodes.name: ATP:L-methionine S-adenosyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Orthophosphate + Diphosphate + S-Adenosyl-L-methionine <=> ATP + L-Methionine + H2O

nodes.name: L-Methionine:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Methionine + H2O + Oxygen <=> 4-Methylthio-2-oxobutanoic acid + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: D-cysteine sulfide-lyase (deaminating

nodes.name: 3-mercaptopyruvate:sulfide sulfurtransferase
nodes.rxn: Mercaptopyruvate + Thioredoxin <=> Hydrogen sulfide + Pyruvate + Thioredoxin disulfide

nodes.name: O-acetyl-L-homoserine acetate-lyase (L-homocysteine forming)
nodes.rxn: O-Acetyl-L-homoserine + Thiosulfate + Thioredoxin + H+ <=> L-Homocysteine + Sulfite + Thioredoxin disulfide + Acetate

nodes.name: gamma-L-glutamyl-L-2-aminobutyrate:glycine ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + gamma-L-Glutamyl-L-2-aminobutyrate + Glycine <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + Ophthalmate

nodes.name: acyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:S-adenosyl-L-methionine acyltranserase (lactone-forming, methylthioadenosine-releasing)
nodes.rxn: Acyl-[acyl-carrier protein] + S-Adenosyl-L-methionine <=> Acyl-carrier protein + 5'-Methylthioadenosine + N-Acyl-L-homoserine lactone

nodes.name: hydrogen sulfide:L-aspartate-4-semialdehyde sulfurtransferase
